{"tid":1048030,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］公司老細迫人去總公司個大老細個親戚既喪禮","createTime":"2019-03-05T11:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T13:00:11.000Z","uid":143448,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5797c5ded311743362042eefc691f66884c3f374","tid":1048030,"uid":143448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"我係間公司其中一個Staff<br />\n冇耐之前<br />\n老細開緊急會議<br />\n以為咩事咁撚心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一開口就講總公司大老細個親戚走左<br />\n某某日子係佢喪禮，必須夾帛金<br />\n所有同事都必須出席<br />\n一講完呢度已經有同事有微言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老細再繼續講落去：「唔去要私下同我親自交代咩原因，我搵唔到有咩理由可以唔出席」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以我老細做野手法：唔去要出證明信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會記名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去喪禮邊有被迫<br />\n我唔知大老細知唔知情啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚去係咪朝早唔使返工<br />\not鐘真係情願留低office做野<br />\n佢冇諗過有人好忌大酒店呢D野<br />\n屋企人忌/怕鬼/周身唔聚財<br />\n迫全體同事集體出席好似拉隊做SHOW咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩好原因同老細講去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（嬲鳩程度冇咁大）？<br />\n有同事用左一早約左人/湊B，不過有人比老細屌鬼咁罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381276e61f5c570abb0419c6d6ea67f4c9432fe1","tid":1048030,"uid":176063,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5813f9c761d07d8c7ccc28c9eb9672c521097b34","tid":1048030,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"份工好緊要?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.